{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/Screenshot_2024-09-20_011435.png?t=1738003587\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Towers &amp; Goblins: The Last Stand&quot; is a fun tower defense game where you plan strategies to fight off crafty goblins.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/Screenshot_2024-09-20_011427.png?t=1738003587\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Resist Goblin Waves</strong>: Fight off various types of goblins to protect your kingdom from destruction. Goblins attack in waves, giving you time to see their approach and prepare your defenses accordingly. Use this interval to strategize and utilize the geographic advantages of your kingdom to enhance your defense.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/New_Project__1_.gif?t=1738003587\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Build and Upgrade</strong>: Construct towers and walls with your resources. Make them stronger to keep goblins out even longer.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/shortest.gif?t=1738003587\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Increase and Manage Population:</strong> Recruit units like pawns and warriors to help expand and defend your kingdom.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/short-units-gif.gif?t=1738003587\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Gather and Manage Resources</strong>: Collect essential resources like wood, stone, and gold. Manage your population and ensure there is enough food to sustain it.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.aka